1
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,820
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:33,312
=Episode 15=
(You should give your all to me,)

3
00:00:33,362 --> 00:00:35,262
(my love.)

4
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:47,560
What are they doing?

5
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,320
You little nerd.

6
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,320
All you ever do is
bury yourself in medical texts.

7
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,680
You'll know when you're older.

8
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:53,640
Let's go.

9
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:54,920
We're leaving?

10
00:00:55,120 --> 00:00:56,520
You can't see this yet.

11
00:00:58,675 --> 00:01:00,762
♪To meet is to overlap♪

12
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,480
Zhao.

13
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,320
Your lips are so soft.

14
00:01:06,375 --> 00:01:12,400
♪Counting every moment,
unwilling to pause♪

15
00:01:14,212 --> 00:01:19,340
♪As raindrops kiss the ground♪

16
00:01:21,487 --> 00:01:26,780
♪Soaking these hazy, drowsy eyes♪

17
00:01:27,750 --> 00:01:29,713
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

18
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:31,612
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

19
00:01:31,612 --> 00:01:34,637
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

20
00:01:34,675 --> 00:01:41,562
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

21
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:04,320
You're sober now?

22
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,520
Then, does what you said just now

23
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,720
still stand?

24
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,720
What I said just now?

25
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,520
It doesn't.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,625
Okay, it does.

27
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,520
It's not meant for you.

28
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,240
It's my birthday.

29
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,640
Are you giving yourself a gift?

30
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,360
If I wear it,

31
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,640
hearing this sound,

32
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:47,600
you'll know I have arrived.

33
00:02:48,137 --> 00:02:49,297
Every step a sound.

34
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,440
Every step a longing.

35
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,720
Such sweet words.

36
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:00,900
Who taught you to speak so?

37
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,320
It must be Bai

38
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:07,440
who reads far too many romance tales.

39
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,480
Was this bell

40
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,720
his idea as well?

41
00:03:12,275 --> 00:03:13,795
I cannot betray a friend.

42
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,480
I wonder how many ladies

43
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,880
Bai will beguile in the future.

44
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,320
Zhao,

45
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,600
let's choose an auspicious day

46
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:29,440
to get married.

47
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:30,000
Okay.

48
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,200
We should also give our child

49
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,040
a name.

50
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,480
Zhao.

51
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,600
Zhao.

52
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,000
Let's name our child

53
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,440
Baobao.

54
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,040
Okay.

55
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,440
Baobao it shall be.

56
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,120
(My mind is made up.)

57
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:13,880
(What can you do to stop me?)

58
00:04:14,925 --> 00:04:17,325
(One month later, Qingxin Pavilion)

59
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,480
(She's pregnant with a demigod.)

60
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,840
(This baby must not remain.)

61
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:54,040
Weren't you on the bed?

62
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,680
Xi.

63
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,560
Xi, are you alright?

64
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,560
I'm fine.

65
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,880
Help him up first.
I'll fetch some medicine for him.

66
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,680
Insolence!

67
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,800
How dare you sleep with a demon?

68
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,560
My mind is made up.

69
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:24,240
In this life,
I will grow old together with Xi.

70
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,120
Humans, gods, and demons

71
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,800
each have their ordained path to follow.

72
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,360
For you to cross races and join with her

73
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,880
is something Heaven cannot abide.

74
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,560
He Xi is now pregnant.

75
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:38,040
This matter will bring endless calamity.

76
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,160
Xi and I...

77
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,600
have a baby?

78
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,480
Since ancient times,

79
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,040
whenever a demigod is born,

80
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:49,480
it brings ruin upon the Three Realms.

81
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,160
This baby cannot be kept.

82
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,800
If you persist in your delusion,

83
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,560
I shall summon heavenly lightning
and strike it down.

84
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,800
But if you

85
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,040
get rid of this ill-fated baby yourself,

86
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:02,040
I will spare you and the demon.

87
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,160
Zhao,

88
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,160
why haven't you helped him up yet?

89
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,560
I am Chu Daqiang.

90
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,560
Thank you for saving my life.

91
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,000
May I ask your name?

92
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,320
My name is He Xi.

93
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,560
I will always

94
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,240
remember your name.

95
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,560
If I should have descendants,

96
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,480
I will name them after you.

97
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,920
You're overstating it.

98
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,560
It was but a small act of kindness.

99
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,920
The battle is intensifying.

100
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,720
I must return
to the battlefield at once.

101
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,440
Take this wound medicine with you.

102
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:48,480
And this blade as well.

103
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,040
It is of little use to me.

104
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,120
You can keep it.

105
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,040
Thank you, Lady He.

106
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,600
I shall take my leave.

107
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,600
Zhao.

108
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,560
What's the matter?

109
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:09,240
Why do you seem so troubled?

110
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,680
Has something happened?

111
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,880
Nothing at all.

112
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,680
Perhaps

113
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,800
you overexerted yourself last night?

114
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,480
What are you saying?

115
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,360
Come try again.

116
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,040
Look at this color.

117
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,040
Does it hurt?

118
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,600
It doesn't.

119
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,480
I'm really fine.

120
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,320
I'm used to it.

121
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,680
(Xi,)

122
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,160
(only by refining
our flesh and blood into an artifact)

123
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:54,720
(and sealing the baby's intelligence)

124
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,320
(can we deceive Heavenly Dao)

125
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,040
(and preserve Baobao.)

126
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,000
(Forgive me.)

127
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:42,560
Since ancient times,

128
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,160
whenever a demigod is born,

129
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:46,520
it brings ruin upon the Three Realms.

130
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,320
This baby cannot be kept.

131
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,800
If you persist in your delusion,

132
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,520
I shall summon heavenly lightning
and strike it down.

133
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:56,080
But if you get rid
of this ill-fated baby yourself,

134
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:59,280
I will spare you and the demon.

135
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:19,440
So this is all your love amounts to.

136
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,400
Today, Zhao

137
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,800
took your baby from you

138
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,680
out of fear of the Heavenly Dao.

139
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,760
Tomorrow, he will

140
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:32,040
destroy you

141
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,440
to save his own life.

142
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:39,800
Cutie,

143
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:43,320
let me help you.

144
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:58,010
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

145
00:10:58,010 --> 00:11:00,590
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

146
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:03,600
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

147
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,230
♪Let the long shadows♪

148
00:11:05,230 --> 00:11:10,510
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

149
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,480
♪If in a dream♪

150
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:15,050
♪I can hear your voice♪

151
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:17,950
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

152
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:20,690
♪Let it be us♪

153
00:11:20,690 --> 00:11:25,180
♪drawing endlessly close♪

154
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,240
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

155
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,570
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

156
00:11:30,110 --> 00:11:32,530
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

157
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:34,480
♪Not even in time♪

158
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:39,910
♪to tell you how I feel♪

159
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:41,680
♪If the rain won't stop♪

160
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:44,430
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

161
00:11:44,430 --> 00:11:47,400
♪Let love go on♪

162
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:49,950
♪Until forever♪

163
00:11:49,950 --> 00:11:54,280
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

164
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:57,040
♪Until forever♪

165
00:11:57,200 --> 00:12:03,990
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
